<!-- TIPS -->
<div class="section" id="tips">
  <div style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--green2);margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">
    <span style="display:block;width:28px;height:1px;background:var(--green2)"></span>Essential notes
  </div>
  <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:36px;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:28px;line-height:1.1">Before you go</h2>
  <div class="tip-grid">
    <div class="tip-card">
      <div class="tip-label">London logistics</div>
      <ul>
        <li>EWR → LHR: arrive 7:15 AM — take the Elizabeth line or Piccadilly line into central London</li>
        <li>Aug 24 concert: The O2 at North Greenwich — take Jubilee line; doors 6:30 PM</li>
        <li>Aug 25: fly from Gatwick (LGW) not Heathrow — Gatwick Express from Victoria, 30 min</li>
        <li>Leave hotel by 7:00 AM on Aug 25 to reach LGW for 9:25 AM flight</li>
        <li>Oyster card or contactless for all London transport</li>
        <li>Book Tower of London, Warner Bros Harry Potter Studio and West End shows in advance</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="tip-card">
      <div class="tip-label">Ariana Grande · The O2</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Aug 24 — Eternal Sunshine Tour · The O2 Arena · Doors 6:30 PM</li>
        <li>Take the Jubilee line to North Greenwich — door-to-door 20 min from central London</li>
        <li>Arrive at the venue 30–45 min before doors for merch and entry queues</li>
        <li>No re-entry once inside the arena</li>
        <li>Buy official merch online before the show — sells out fast at venue</li>
        <li>Keep the morning of Aug 25 light — early airport transfer to LGW at 7 AM</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="tip-card">
      <div class="tip-label">Switzerland tips</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Get a Zürich Card (24h CHF 29 / 72h CHF 59) — free public transport + museum entry</li>
        <li>Swiss franc (CHF) — Zurich is one of the world's most expensive cities; budget CHF 80–150/day</li>
        <li>Many museums closed Mondays — Aug 25 is Tuesday, all good</li>
        <li>Fondue is mandatory: try Zürich Chuchi or Zebra Bistro</li>
        <li>ZRH → FCO: easyJet departs 8:30 AM Aug 27 — leave hotel by 6:30 AM</li>
        <li>Lindt Chocolate Museum: book online — tickets sell out weeks ahead</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="tip-card">
      <div class="tip-label">Packing & practical</div>
      <ul>
        <li>UK uses Type G plugs; Switzerland uses Type J — both different from US Type A/B</li>
        <li>Currency: GBP in London, CHF in Switzerland; EUR not accepted</li>
        <li>London weather in August: 18–24°C, occasional showers — pack a light layer</li>
        <li>Concert outfit: The O2 has no coat check — dress for the show and a warm exit</li>
        <li>This is Part I of II — the Italy + Istanbul trip follows immediately Aug 27</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
