      { time: '6:30 PM', name: '★ Ariana Grande — The Eternal Sunshine Tour', note: 'Doors open 6:30 PM at The O2 Arena. This is her first UK tour in six years — the Eternal Sunshine Tour supports her seventh studio album. The O2 holds 20,000 people; expect a full production show with the Eternal Sunshine and Brighter Days Ahead setlist.', tag_concert: 'The O2, North Greenwich · Doors 6:30 PM' },
